"2050500217" and "Rev:1.0" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :The same text is found on the [[Nexxt Solutions Viking 150 (ARN01154U4)]], :[[SMC SMCWBR14S-N5 rev A2]] and [[Rosewill RNX-N150RT v2]] boards.
The sample SSID shown in the FCC manual is ''PLANET_WNRT-617''.
This device is assumed to use a 00:30:4F (''PLANET Technology Corporation'') OUI. :It's on the FCC EUT's label..
The power adapter shown in the FCC photos is a '''VASATA''' :P090060-2B1 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.3A -> 9VDC, 0.6A).
